{"tid":1695402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民運動日好唔好？","createTime":"2019-11-05T15:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T15:26:34.000Z","uid":244786,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f55c8367c3e33c02d7b316be9ce09acfae8d6b","tid":1695402,"uid":244786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"相信大家近排都冇咩時間做運動，假如嚟個全民運動日 做啲平時少見嘅運動好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n首先就有棒球 <br />\n棒球呢個活動真喺喺香港好少見，假如嚟個百萬人棒球日相信都幾龐大<br />\n<br />\n或者板球，呢個活動好似幾受啲少數族裔歡迎，例如[<span style=\"color: red;\">red]印度</span>，南亞[/red]（By Wikipedia) 我哋又可以connect多次 <br />\n<br />\n最後仲可以嚟個網球大師賽（地點大家喜歡）， 又或者到時可以一齊練習開波嘅姿勢，或者射波嘅姿勢。<br />\n<br />\n我真喺未見到有邊個國家或者地區試過嚟個百萬人運動日 如果真喺可以成功舉辦唔知會唔會又衝上國際呢？<br />\n仲有咩建議都可以提出討論！"},{"pid":"7df060e6fec8cf9c1528720e73ebf51b617fc3d9","tid":1695402,"uid":244786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cf0488b642e3157404d9c93f483f31f918fb02f4","tid":1695402,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"快閃捉伊因"},{"pid":"3d28d8eac4058162acf929808931e310d0130a4a","tid":1695402,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7VgAdvv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7VgAdvv.jpg&h=484c77ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE66GT2NXnPQ_tqDaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAE66GT2NXnPQ_tqDaA&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGIhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=b4237a7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE66GT2NXnPQ_tqDaA</a>"},{"pid":"6ef594960f9df94594344368b2ba418dffd435c6","tid":1695402,"uid":244786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf0488b642e3157404d9c93f483f31f918fb02f4","tid":1695402,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:15:57.000Z","msg":